<subSubSection pageId="0" pageNumber="31" type="remarks">
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="31">Remark.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="31">
This is the first report of this species from China. The position of Sc relative to Rs and female body color shows the geographic variation. First, specimens from Xinjiang (Burqin, Altay Mountain) have Sc1 slightly beyond basal Rs, Sc2 reaching 1/5 of Rs (Fig. 
<figureCitation captionStart="Figures 1–3" captionStartId="F1" captionText="Figures 1 - 3. Limonia macrostigma, male 1 habitus, lateral view 2 head and thorax, dorsal view 3 right wing. Scale bars: 1.0 mm." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.971.35875.figures1-3" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/456132" pageId="0" pageNumber="31">3</figureCitation>
), similar wing venation with 
<normalizedToken originalValue="Savchenko’s">Savchenko's</normalizedToken>
drawing (
<bibRefCitation author="Savchenko, EN" journalOrPublisher="Fauna Ukrainy" pageId="0" pageNumber="31" pagination="1 - 180" refId="B17" refString="Savchenko, EN, 1985. Komary-limoniidy [limoniid-flies]. Subfamily Limoniinae. Fauna Ukrainy 14 (4): 1 - 180" title="Komary-limoniidy [limoniid-flies]. Subfamily Limoniinae." volume="14" year="1985">Savchenko 1985</bibRefCitation>
: 145, fig. 95.2), whereas specimens from Korea have Sc1 reaching 1/3 of Rs, Sc2 reaching 1/4 of Rs (
<bibRefCitation DOI="https://doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.4231.1.1" author="Podenas, S" journalOrPublisher="Zootaxa" pageId="0" pageNumber="31" pagination="1 - 37" refId="B15" refString="Podenas, S, Podeniene, V, 2017. Limonia crane flies (Diptera: Limoniidae) of Korea. Zootaxa 4231 (1): 1 - 37, DOI: https://doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.4231.1.1" title="Limonia crane flies (Diptera: Limoniidae) of Korea." url="https://doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.4231.1.1" volume="4231" year="2017">Podenas and Podeniene 2017</bibRefCitation>
: 17, fig. 25). Moreover, female specimens from Xinjiang have the dark brown sternites, whereas Korean specimens have the yellow sternites (
<bibRefCitation DOI="https://doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.4231.1.1" author="Podenas, S" journalOrPublisher="Zootaxa" pageId="0" pageNumber="31" pagination="1 - 37" refId="B15" refString="Podenas, S, Podeniene, V, 2017. Limonia crane flies (Diptera: Limoniidae) of Korea. Zootaxa 4231 (1): 1 - 37, DOI: https://doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.4231.1.1" title="Limonia crane flies (Diptera: Limoniidae) of Korea." url="https://doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.4231.1.1" volume="4231" year="2017">Podenas and Podeniene 2017</bibRefCitation>
:19).
</paragraph>
